{"tid":1310900,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(升級) 唔好再叫(黑警，可恥)得唔得？","createTime":"2019-07-13T02:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T04:39:12.000Z","uid":14908,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60e1780bfd2440aff95d9f95399a7145c4f7d4da","tid":1310900,"uid":14908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:10:37.000Z","msg":"要升級包圍口號都要升級<br />\n林鄭月娥就屌你老母<br />\n黑警就死全家<br />\n佢話唔好禍及家人<br />\n就更加要禍及<br />\n知道香港人係好多有政治潔癖<br />\n但我地只要多人一齊嗌就大把人跟<br />\n香港警察係唔撚知法架<br />\n唔再叫法咩法犯啦求下大家<br />\n請幫推!"},{"pid":"81c591bc97037e7dafd4e8903daad2d62d7f5c62","tid":1310900,"uid":8833,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"唔夠挑釁<br />\n可以再狠d"},{"pid":"47d527f5b1dd39bc38fb4d2830afc88ca0035901","tid":1310900,"uid":205339,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"黑警 死全家<br />\n起你底咪起你底"},{"pid":"28359ccaf30a79a4a08fc4853ef1e829d50d20a6","tid":1310900,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d527f5b1dd39bc38fb4d2830afc88ca0035901","tid":1310900,"uid":205339,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"黑警 死全家<br />\n起你底咪起你底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e5587875bdd6cb88db0490b68f9df26b886772","tid":1310900,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"427732a50234a80893c710d14234fd56bf096626","tid":1310900,"uid":277114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:41:27.000Z","msg"